簡單的繪圖 (使用ggplot2)

散佈圖

library(ggplot2)
ggplot(CO2, aes(x = conc, y = uptake, color = Plant)) +
  geom_point() +
  ggtitle("Carbon Dioxide Uptake in Grass Plants")

線圖

ggplot(women, aes(x = weight, y= height))+
   geom_point()+
   ggtitle("Average Heights and Weights for American Women")+
   geom_line()

直方圖

ggplot(trees, aes(x = Volume)) +
  ggtitle("Girth, Height and Volume for Black Cherry Trees")+
  geom_histogram(binwidth =30)

盒鬚圖

ggplot(CO2, aes(x = Type, y = uptake)) +
  ggtitle("Carbon Dioxide Uptake in Grass Plants")+
  geom_boxplot()

長條圖

ggplot(quakes, aes(x = depth))+
  ggtitle("Locations of Earthquakes off Fiji")+
  geom_bar()
